</title>
<subSubSection id="CF2D443B94783474FAEDE9A1D87B27BC" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" type="description">
<paragraph id="4674780B87B68B8D2D004848B4DB7654" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
Wuchsform und Zweige wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="6E98E0FD2E2EED8C0F04903E390A0822" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="retusa">
<emphasis id="A2FDB5755EDB3EBCEFE77DDDA476C3DD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. retusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3). 
<normalizedToken id="7D138B2F051FF9ABACDE7D7E32F3DF59" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A3C000825C2821737A7A889388E7DE33" originalValue="ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">aehnlich</normalizedToken>
denen von 
<taxonomicName id="7A5ABDD565A5F686E664F38D63203D39" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="retusa">
<emphasis id="C51C6007BCB6146E5C2EE55180D72616" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. retusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, jedoch 
<emphasis id="6C358E954B633B387F22C73C37CBA713" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">0,2-0,8 cm lang</emphasis>
, meist 2mal so lang wie breit, oval, 
<normalizedToken id="C1EA3AA33604EB7A59FE1AF18390D309" originalValue="größte" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">groesste</normalizedToken>
Breite 
<normalizedToken id="136AC65B855F281FBCF9C982AA5ADDCF" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">ueber</normalizedToken>
oder in der Mitte, 
<taxonomicName id="D7429E2CB574257921972DABC2F3C1B6" authority="den Grund" authorityName="den Grund" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Sporn" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="gegen">gegen den Grund</taxonomicName>
hin 
<normalizedToken id="7FA09FDB542D693B130CD12080A53AE2" originalValue="keilförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">keilfoermig</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D1C08587486BE36069441335AB3CED9E" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
, an der Spitze 
<emphasis id="A73E6CF72F35D4189BDAB567927C5CF2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">stumpf oder abgerundet</emphasis>
, selten ausgerandet, 
<emphasis id="29317DE179F5E745117C98779D97EF09" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
meist ohne 
<normalizedToken id="E831A4099E06CA329794CB29D08F9D4F" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Blattstiel etwa 1 mm lang. 
<normalizedToken id="AFC14C4CB30AA4671D3769E8C2901639" originalValue="Blütenstände" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Bluetenstaende</normalizedToken>
erscheinen nach den 
<normalizedToken id="96B4161452C148E863A6B4C309A20728" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="999174BD6A5FA93B95EC2F969152FCE3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
<normalizedToken id="FF004ED9F2950FEBA0689656AB1BC985" originalValue="Staubfäden" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Staubfaeden</normalizedToken>
etwa 2mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="E1CAC37630CEEC85B040EDC6E8BFA6ED" originalValue="Tragblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Tragblaetter</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="7EFA5FC8395387327A16FF1AF9DC5D04" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
2-3 mm lang
</emphasis>
. 
<normalizedToken id="521E39CCE754C66DC6781B41D7568B6C" originalValue="Übrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Uebrige</normalizedToken>
Merkmale wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="9CCA96E065134D7949ED18E0807BD660" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="retusa">
<emphasis id="B1C0FF54ABA09E9AFD8C1E426EEF1EEC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. retusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3F75E26F16EF98360483EEAFAFC41EB4" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
<emphasis id="E0D0387648349852A9FE2107414EB7F6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E5AE2AE15CDCE232A51DB86EE980A85" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
<emphasis id="E53AE35F3521C59FC95A6F096289E6DD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin. 
<normalizedToken id="3CB1EA52A04605402F727248961A8894" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="2E061C5E7650AA732571CBD30E3B99CE" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="reticulata">
<emphasis id="C5F56EEE3A984D5A8F936FC69731616E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. reticulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1), nur auf Kalk, oft Pionier auf unbesiedelten 
<normalizedToken id="92266A9DE46218D8F64374844C99A628" originalValue="Rohböden" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Rohboeden</normalizedToken>
und deshalb meist in exponierteren Lagen als 
<taxonomicName id="6046AA4925B0F01D031B87EFC66140C2" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="reticulata">
<emphasis id="CFACF645AD26AF1D17A2BCEC344D900F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. reticulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="69C06D8BEC4C0FA48A881F250AF1017E" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
<emphasis id="907CC903189E810827837959A629A94D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Nicht genau bekannt. 
<emphasis id="55C36759B3264C8E44F840B4EE7275AD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Alpen-Pflanze</emphasis>
: Zentral- und Ostalpen, Apennin. - Im Gebiet: Alpen, ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="396C79EEDF9CB513220CA5F89FB9E071" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DF305DCF39405C9646ED636E49892316" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">
<emphasis id="08E0E5D8A0F31EA15048FCED8196D933" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Man findet gelegentlich 
<normalizedToken id="849A1D5CB53ABAB6E647CD6E0B1CADA9" originalValue="Übergangsformen" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">Uebergangsformen</normalizedToken>
zwischen 
<taxonomicName id="49D2D4FC42391E439E9E6BFCE69B271F" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="retusa">
<emphasis id="B36E1D89FCC3D9C1306AA7F656CCE8A3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. retusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="A052AF16491F50F7AFF49AE7E8ECC37D" class="Ascidiacea" family="Polycitoridae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aplousobranchia" pageId="null" pageNumber="658" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="serpyllifolia">
<emphasis id="47091C9DA316828F7F9F147E77BEC782" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="658">S. serpyllifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Beide Arten aus dem Alpengebiet sollten experimentell untersucht werden.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
